          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "The only surviving example of a 1938  Mercedes-Benz 540k Autobahnkurier with 5.4-liter power has just clinched the Best in Show award during 2019's Amelia Island Concours d’Elegance",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          }
        ],
        "direction": "ltr",
        "format": "",
        "indent": 0,
        "type": "koenig-heading",
        "tag": "h3",
        "version": 1,
        "renderVersion": "4.0"
      },
      {
        "children": [
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "The winner of Florida’s Amelia Island Concours d’Elegance 2019 has been announced! The cosseted title of Best in Show was awarded to the final-production 1938 ",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "children": [
              {
                "detail": 0,
                "format": 0,
                "mode": "normal",
                "style": "",
                "text": "Mercedes-Benz ",
                "type": "text",
                "version": 1
              }
            ],
            "direction": "ltr",
            "format": "",
            "indent": 0,
            "type": "link",
            "rel": null,
            "target": null,
            "title": null,
            "url": "__GHOST_URL__/articles/all/1973-mercedes-benz-280c/",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "540K Autobahnkurier.",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          }
        ],
        "direction": "ltr",
        "format": "",
        "indent": 0,
        "type": "paragraph",
        "version": 1
      },
      {
        "children": [
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "Only six examples of the Mercedes-Benz 540K Autobahnkurier – so named after the new highways across and around Berlin – were crafted for Europe’s social elite before the outbreak of WWII.",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          }
        ],
        "direction": "ltr",
        "format": "",
        "indent": 0,
        "type": "paragraph",
        "version": 1
      },
      {
        "children": [
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "Of the six vehicles built, four were installed with a 5-liter powerplant while the remaining two were blessed with Mercedes’ 5.4-liter eight-cylinder engine. The Amelia Island Concours winner remains the sole survivor from these two examples.",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          }
        ],
        "direction": "ltr",
        "format": "",
        "indent": 0,
        "type": "paragraph",
        "version": 1
      },
      {
        "children": [
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "More From Mercedes!",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "type": "linebreak",
            "version": 1
          }
        ],
        "direction": "ltr",
        "format": "",
        "indent": 0,
        "type": "koenig-heading",
        "tag": "h2",
        "version": 1,
        "renderVersion": "4.0"
      },
      {
        "children": [
          {
            "children": [
              {
                "children": [
                  {
                    "detail": 0,
                    "format": 0,
